data.description: Welcome To Your New Home! Amazing location Minutes From Downtown Morristown. This Perfect All ONE LEVEL LIVING Rancher Sits On A Large Flat Corner Lot In A Mature, Peaceful, Subdivision. This Entire Home Has Been  Tastefully Painted In Warm Neutral Tones & Has All New Beautiful Laminate Floors Throughout! The Large Open Kitchen Has  Plenty Of Cabinets, Great Counter Space And An Eat-In Area. Every Room Is Spacious Including The Livingroom W/Adjacent Dining /Flex Room . There Are 3 Large Bedrooms, & 2 Full Tiled  Baths, With An Abundance Of Spacious Closets & Numerous Storage Spaces. Enjoy The Ease Of A Loop Driveway  That Will Accommodate Several Vehicles. Additionally, The outdoor Storage Building Is Just The Right Size For A Craft Room Or Wok Shop.* Windows, Gutters, & Electrical panel Replaced In 2021 & A Newer HVAC.Don't Hesitate This One Won't Last
